gh-utils-lenik (1.4.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * auto-detect project type (debian/vsix/nodejs)
  * support VSIX extensions and Node.js packages
  * determine version from changelog or package.json
  * build with debuild or pnpm package based on type
  * attach appropriate artifacts (.deb, .vsix, -dist.zip)

